    "correct": "According to American Cancer Society, all men over the age of 50 years should undergo annual PSA measurement and digital rectal examination (DRE). This recommendtion is fur-ther supplemented by the guidelines from American Urological Association to start screen-ing 10 years earlier in high-risk individuals (cau-casians with family history of prostate cancer and African Americans).",
